WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

2
00:00:30.697 --> 00:00:35.786
- Hail Mary. full of grace.
the Lord is with thee.

3
00:00:36.453 --> 00:00:39.706
Blessed art thou among women.

4
00:00:39.748 --> 00:00:42.167
and blessed is the fruit
of thy womb Jesus.

5
00:00:43.752 --> 00:00:48.423
Holy Mary. Mother of God.
pray for us sinners.

6
00:00:53.178 --> 00:00:55.514
Now and at the hour of our death.

7
00:00:57.099 --> 00:00:58.892
Amen.

8
00:03:15.737 --> 00:03:17.781
No. no.

9
00:03:25.205 --> 00:03:26.957
No. no!

10
00:03:32.879 --> 00:03:35.340
No. no. no!

11
00:04:03.618 --> 00:04:05.078
No!

12
00:04:09.791 --> 00:04:11.585
Help!

13
00:04:19.968 --> 00:04:21.261
Help!

14
00:04:22.471 --> 00:04:24.222
Help!

15
00:04:25.849 --> 00:04:28.602
No. no. no!

16
00:04:28.643 --> 00:04:30.437
Help!

17
00:04:45.660 --> 00:04:47.662
Please...

18
00:04:49.498 --> 00:04:51.750
...help.

19
00:04:53.877 --> 00:04:55.420
No!

20
00:05:02.093 --> 00:05:04.221
Help!

21
00:05:36.253 --> 00:05:39.130
- I'm sorry.
but how much longer will this take?

22
00:05:39.172 --> 00:05:40.841
I've got to take
my vows tonight.

23
00:05:40.882 --> 00:05:43.301
and I really can't be late.

24
00:05:43.343 --> 00:05:45.178
Do you speak English?

25
00:05:45.220 --> 00:05:47.556
- Sorry for the wait.

26
00:05:47.597 --> 00:05:49.724
It's extra work now
when someone arrives

27
00:05:49.766 --> 00:05:52.227
without a return ticket.

28
00:05:52.269 --> 00:05:54.813
Parli italiano?

29
00:05:54.855 --> 00:05:57.065
I ask if
you're learning Italian.

30
00:05:57.107 --> 00:06:00.735
- Oh. I'm trying. but it's
a lot harder than I thought.

31
00:06:00.777 --> 00:06:02.988
- Mm.

32
00:06:03.029 --> 00:06:06.575
So this convent.
they bought you the ticket?

33
00:06:06.616 --> 00:06:07.951
- Mm-hmm.

34
00:06:11.204 --> 00:06:14.416
- You're very young to
be a nun. aren't you?

35
00:06:15.000 --> 00:06:16.334
- What a waste.

36
00:06:17.294 --> 00:06:18.879
Look at her.

37
00:06:19.170 --> 00:06:21.172
- It's a different life. yeah?

38
00:06:21.214 --> 00:06:24.259
It must have been
a hard decision.

39
00:06:25.719 --> 00:06:29.389
- I don't think
of it like that.

40
00:06:29.431 --> 00:06:31.516
as a decision.

41
00:06:35.186 --> 00:06:37.063
- Very well.

42
00:06:38.189 --> 00:06:42.152
I hope you find what you're
looking for. Sister Cecilia.

43
00:06:57.000 --> 00:06:58.793
- Sister Cecilia.

44
00:06:58.835 --> 00:06:59.878
Apologies.

45
00:06:59.920 --> 00:07:01.630
I'm Deacon Enzo. Come with me.

46
00:07:01.671 --> 00:07:03.632
- Thank you.

47
00:07:37.415 --> 00:07:38.291
- How much longer?

48
00:07:38.750 --> 00:07:40.126
- We're almost there.

49
00:08:27.549 --> 00:08:28.967
Right this way. Sister Cecilia.

50
00:08:39.561 --> 00:08:40.854
- Sister Cecilia!

51
00:08:41.438 --> 00:08:43.231
- Reverend Mother.

52
00:08:44.524 --> 00:08:47.902
- Your eyes radiate
the light of the Holy Spirit.

53
00:08:48.445 --> 00:08:51.489
Like the angels delivered you
straight from the heavens.

54
00:08:51.906 --> 00:08:54.409
We've been eagerly awaiting your arrival.
my dear.

55
00:08:55.118 --> 00:08:56.745
- I'm sorry.

56
00:08:58.788 --> 00:09:00.790
- She says you're pretty.

57
00:09:00.832 --> 00:09:03.668
- Grazie.
I'm Sister Cecilia.

58
00:09:05.003 --> 00:09:06.254
- Isabelle.

59
00:09:06.880 --> 00:09:09.507
- Isabelle. will you please
show Cecilia to her room?

60
00:09:09.883 --> 00:09:12.761
- I have to help our sisters get ready
for tonight's celebration.

61
00:09:12.802 --> 00:09:15.013
- Mind your place and do as I ask!

62
00:09:17.390 --> 00:09:20.435
- Let me show you to your room.

63
00:09:20.477 --> 00:09:23.938
Our Lady of Sorrows
was founded in 1632

64
00:09:23.980 --> 00:09:25.815
as a refuge for elder sisters

65
00:09:25.857 --> 00:09:27.776
before their transition
to heaven.

66
00:09:27.817 --> 00:09:29.736
- It's really beautiful.
- Yes. it is.

67
00:09:29.778 --> 00:09:31.279
Buongiorno. sorelle.

68
00:09:31.321 --> 00:09:33.281
And we work hard
to keep it that way.

69
00:09:33.323 --> 00:09:35.075
Our sister's final
days should be

70
00:09:35.116 --> 00:09:37.827
a pleasing environment
to help distract from all

71
00:09:37.869 --> 00:09:39.996
the sickness and suffering.

72
00:09:40.038 --> 00:09:43.124
All of this. it was built on
the catacomb of St. Stephen.

73
00:09:43.166 --> 00:09:44.793
- Catacombs?

74
00:09:44.834 --> 00:09:46.795
- It's off limits.

75
00:09:47.754 --> 00:09:48.963
Hello. Sisters.

76
00:09:49.005 --> 00:09:50.965
This is our new novice. Sister Cecilia.

77
00:09:51.007 --> 00:09:52.467
- Ciao.

78
00:09:52.509 --> 00:09:54.844
- The one in the wheelchair.
her tumor has metastasized.

79
00:09:54.886 --> 00:09:57.722
So we expect her to meet God
by the end of the week.

80
00:09:57.764 --> 00:10:00.350
- You talk about it
so casually.

81
00:10:00.391 --> 00:10:03.103
- Death is a part
of everyday life here.

82
00:10:04.562 --> 00:10:06.147
- Have you seen my daddy?

83
00:10:06.731 --> 00:10:10.360
- Yes. let's go find him. shall we?

84
00:10:11.152 --> 00:10:13.530
It's best to just play along
with their delusions

85
00:10:13.571 --> 00:10:15.281
unless they get violent.

86
00:10:15.323 --> 00:10:17.450
Be careful of this one.
She bites.

87
00:10:39.180 --> 00:10:41.850
- I'm sorry.

88
00:10:41.891 --> 00:10:43.852
- Living quarters
for the caretakers

89
00:10:43.893 --> 00:10:45.728
are down there and upstairs.

90
00:10:45.770 --> 00:10:47.647
Morning prayer begins
at 5:00 a.m..

91
00:10:47.689 --> 00:10:49.107
communal meal is after.

92
00:10:49.149 --> 00:10:51.109
And if you have any
dietary restrictions.

93
00:10:51.151 --> 00:10:52.944
we cannot accommodate them.

94
00:10:52.986 --> 00:10:56.197
And this room is yours.

95
00:11:00.493 --> 00:11:02.036
- Thank you. Sister.

96
00:11:02.078 --> 00:11:04.581
I feel honored
to serve alongside you.

97
00:11:04.622 --> 00:11:06.249
- You're very sweet.

98
00:11:06.291 --> 00:11:07.709
- Thank you.

99
00:11:07.750 --> 00:11:09.335
- I don't mean that
as a compliment.

100
00:11:10.879 --> 00:11:14.090
I'm sure this must
feel very romantic.

101
00:11:14.132 --> 00:11:15.925
but this is our life.

102
00:11:15.967 --> 00:11:17.802
And I promise you.
work is hard.

103
00:11:17.844 --> 00:11:19.512
physically and emotionally.

104
00:11:19.554 --> 00:11:20.680
So if you're here
to find yourself.

105
00:11:20.722 --> 00:11:21.681
there are easier ways.

106
00:11:21.723 --> 00:11:23.224
- I'm not.

107
00:11:26.603 --> 00:11:30.106
- Tonight. you do not
have to take your vows.

108
00:11:30.148 --> 00:11:33.735
You can still go back.
and God will forgive you.

109
00:11:35.820 --> 00:11:38.698
- I think he has
sufficiently prepared me.

110
00:11:43.995 --> 00:11:47.624
- The ceremony will start
at 1700 in the chapel.

111
00:11:47.665 --> 00:11:49.250
Don't be late.

112
00:11:57.592 --> 00:11:59.677
- Oh. ciao.
- Ciao.

113
00:11:59.719 --> 00:12:01.888
I'm sorry.
- No. it's fine.

114
00:12:01.930 --> 00:12:03.389
- I'm Cecilia.

115
00:12:03.431 --> 00:12:05.558
- Oh. I'm Guendalina.
You can call me Gwen.

116
00:12:05.600 --> 00:12:07.018
My room is there.

117
00:12:07.060 --> 00:12:09.020
Where in the States
are you from?

118
00:12:09.062 --> 00:12:11.522
- Just outside
of Detroit. Michigan.

119
00:12:11.564 --> 00:12:12.732
- Mm-hmm.

120
00:12:12.774 --> 00:12:14.525
-Are you
from around here or...

121
00:12:14.567 --> 00:12:16.903
- Closer to Milan.

122
00:12:18.071 --> 00:12:19.781
You're far from home.

123
00:12:19.822 --> 00:12:22.825
- Yeah. my parish closed.

124
00:12:22.867 --> 00:12:24.285
- Did the priest
get in trouble?

125
00:12:24.327 --> 00:12:25.703
- No.

126
00:12:25.745 --> 00:12:27.997
No. no. no. no. no. no.
nothing. nothing like that.

127
00:12:28.039 --> 00:12:30.458
Just low attendance.

128
00:12:30.500 --> 00:12:33.419
And that church was
my family. my home.

129
00:12:33.461 --> 00:12:35.546
Leaving. I felt pretty lost.

130
00:12:35.588 --> 00:12:38.633
But then Father Tedeschi.
he reached out to me.

131
00:12:38.675 --> 00:12:39.842
- Yeah.

132
00:12:39.884 --> 00:12:42.011
He has a talent.

133
00:12:43.805 --> 00:12:46.349
Sniffing out broken birds.

134
00:12:52.522 --> 00:12:54.816
Oh. I didn't want
to offend you.

135
00:12:54.857 --> 00:12:59.654
I think that maybe we are all
head cases or runaways.

136
00:13:01.531 --> 00:13:03.449
- Which one are you?

137
00:13:06.077 --> 00:13:07.954
- Both.

138
00:13:09.789 --> 00:13:12.166
Next time if you want.
you can lock the door.

139
00:13:12.208 --> 00:13:13.876
- Thanks.

140
00:14:34.916 --> 00:14:36.626
- Sister Cecilia.

141
00:14:36.667 --> 00:14:40.630
- Father Tedeschi. it's nice
to meet you in person.

142
00:14:40.671 --> 00:14:44.467
- We all feel so blessed
to have you here.

143
00:14:44.509 --> 00:14:47.095
How's the Italian
coming along?

144
00:14:47.136 --> 00:14:48.346
- Comme ci. com me ci.

145
00:14:48.388 --> 00:14:49.639
It's fine.

146
00:14:49.680 --> 00:14:51.224
I will translate for you.

147
00:14:59.273 --> 00:15:04.570
- In the name of the Father.
the Son. and the Holy Spirit.

148
00:15:04.612 --> 00:15:06.406
All: Amen.

149
00:15:22.130 --> 00:15:26.509
- Let us rejoice. for the marriage
of the Lamb has come.

150
00:15:26.551 --> 00:15:30.972
and his brides have
made themselves ready.

151
00:15:37.103 --> 00:15:38.438
- Sorella Cecilia.

152
00:15:38.479 --> 00:15:40.356
- Sister Cecilia.

153
00:15:46.487 --> 00:15:48.573
- Do you promise
to follow Christ

154
00:15:48.614 --> 00:15:51.033
more closely
by living a life devoid

155
00:15:51.075 --> 00:15:53.077
of material possessions?

156
00:15:53.119 --> 00:15:56.164
Do you promise to free
yourself from the demands

157
00:15:56.205 --> 00:15:59.876
of a human relationship
and follow with joy

158
00:15:59.917 --> 00:16:02.795
when he shall come again--

159
00:16:02.837 --> 00:16:06.883
A vow of poverty.
chastity. and obedience?

160
00:16:06.924 --> 00:16:08.217
- I do.

161
00:16:16.225 --> 00:16:19.812
- May God give you the
strength to fulfill your vows

162
00:16:19.854 --> 00:16:22.940
faithfully and joyfully.

163
00:16:22.982 --> 00:16:27.236
May you shine his light
for the world to see.

164
00:16:33.826 --> 00:16:35.620
- How are you feeling?

165
00:16:35.661 --> 00:16:38.080
- Full.

166
00:16:38.122 --> 00:16:40.625
- Yeah. we don't--
we don't really have anything

167
00:16:40.666 --> 00:16:42.543
like this back home.

168
00:16:42.585 --> 00:16:44.879
- Cecilia. this is your home.

169
00:16:47.215 --> 00:16:48.925
I know. I know.

170
00:16:48.966 --> 00:16:50.843
I felt the same way
when I started here.

171
00:16:50.885 --> 00:16:53.513
I didn't grow up
wanting to be a priest.

172
00:16:53.554 --> 00:16:58.851
My first career was
in sciences. biology.

173
00:16:58.893 --> 00:17:02.480
I was almost two decades in.
and I couldn't

174
00:17:02.522 --> 00:17:04.190
understand the world
any better than back

175
00:17:04.232 --> 00:17:06.526
when I was in Sunday school.

176
00:17:06.567 --> 00:17:10.613
And then God showed me a path.

177
00:17:10.655 --> 00:17:12.740
He brought me here.

178
00:17:12.782 --> 00:17:14.700
This is where I
was meant to be.

179
00:17:20.873 --> 00:17:22.250
I'm sorry.
I'm so sorry.

180
00:17:22.291 --> 00:17:24.293
Two glasses in and I can't
stop talking about myself.

181
00:17:24.335 --> 00:17:25.711
I'm so sorry.
- No. it's OK.

182
00:17:25.753 --> 00:17:27.880
It's OK.
- What about you?

183
00:17:27.922 --> 00:17:30.132
I imagine it was
a difficult decision.

184
00:17:30.174 --> 00:17:35.846
- I mean. yes.
it seemed so far away.

185
00:17:35.888 --> 00:17:39.642
But the opportunities
back in the States.

186
00:17:39.684 --> 00:17:43.229
I didn't feel like
that's what God saved me for.

187
00:17:45.189 --> 00:17:46.649
- If it's too personal--

188
00:17:46.691 --> 00:17:47.942
- No.

189
00:17:47.984 --> 00:17:52.280
When I was 12 years old.
there was this part

190
00:17:52.321 --> 00:17:56.492
of the Saginaw River
that would always freeze over.

191
00:17:56.534 --> 00:17:58.828
And no matter how
cold it was. I would

192
00:17:58.869 --> 00:18:00.788
always walk out onto the ice.

193
00:18:00.830 --> 00:18:02.915
And I would do this thing
where I took my gloves off.

194
00:18:02.957 --> 00:18:06.711
and I would place my hands
right on the ice.

195
00:18:06.752 --> 00:18:08.170
And I would hold
them there until I

196
00:18:08.212 --> 00:18:11.132
couldn't feel anything.

197
00:18:11.173 --> 00:18:13.634
I don't remember
the ice breaking.

198
00:18:13.676 --> 00:18:17.179
I just. I remember
this sharp pain of cold.

199
00:18:20.349 --> 00:18:21.684
The paramedics.
they tried to revive me.

200
00:18:21.726 --> 00:18:23.978
but my heart stopped
for almost seven minutes.

201
00:18:25.021 --> 00:18:27.648
- That sounds terrifying.

202
00:18:29.233 --> 00:18:32.069
- I know God saved
me for a reason. but...

203
00:18:32.111 --> 00:18:34.655
I guess I'm still searching
for what that reason is.

204
00:18:39.619 --> 00:18:43.122
Now will you--
will you excuse me. please?

205
00:19:25.831 --> 00:19:27.875
- Ciao?

206
00:20:23.764 --> 00:20:25.391
- Are you OK?

207
00:20:34.191 --> 00:20:36.902
I'll go get some help.

208
00:20:36.944 --> 00:20:39.113
- Cecilia.

209
00:20:39.155 --> 00:20:41.407
- Reverend Mother.
I'm so sorry.

210
00:20:41.449 --> 00:20:43.534
I heard her crying and--

211
00:20:43.576 --> 00:20:44.827
- It's OK.

212
00:20:45.119 --> 00:20:47.663
Sometimes we get caught up in emotion.

213
00:20:48.748 --> 00:20:50.750
You have a question.

214
00:20:50.791 --> 00:20:52.626
All right.

215
00:20:59.467 --> 00:21:01.844
- What is this place?

216
00:21:10.644 --> 00:21:13.481
- Saint Helena. Mother of Constantine...

217
00:21:14.023 --> 00:21:15.733
...brought this back from Jerusalem.

218
00:21:16.942 --> 00:21:17.777
Here.

219
00:21:22.865 --> 00:21:24.867
He suffered on the cross.

220
00:21:33.709 --> 00:21:35.544
- Suffered? This is the--

221
00:21:39.507 --> 00:21:41.050
- Yes.

222
00:21:41.759 --> 00:21:46.764
For you. For us.
For our sins. For our salvation.

223
00:21:47.473 --> 00:21:49.308
We suffer.

224
00:21:49.892 --> 00:21:51.685
In the name of His love.

225
00:21:53.062 --> 00:21:54.146
It is a gift.

226
00:21:55.648 --> 00:21:58.609
Suffering is love.

227
00:22:02.446 --> 00:22:03.864
Are you alright. Sister?

228
00:22:17.753 --> 00:22:20.172
- In the name of the Father
and the Son

229
00:22:20.214 --> 00:22:21.465
and the Holy Spirit.

230
00:22:21.507 --> 00:22:22.883
Amen.

231
00:22:22.925 --> 00:22:26.053
Bless me. Father.
for I have sinned.

232
00:22:26.095 --> 00:22:28.556
It's been three days
since my last confession.

233
00:22:32.059 --> 00:22:35.479
I was--

234
00:22:35.521 --> 00:22:37.898
I was careless last night.

235
00:22:40.067 --> 00:22:44.280
I must have drank too much
wine and embarrassed myself

236
00:22:44.321 --> 00:22:46.240
in front of Mother Superior.

237
00:22:54.373 --> 00:22:57.209
I promise to carry myself with
grace because I want nothing

238
00:22:57.251 --> 00:23:00.170
more than to belong here.

239
00:23:00.212 --> 00:23:02.590
I'm afraid I've already
messed things up.

240
00:23:08.512 --> 00:23:11.390
I'm sorry for these...

241
00:23:18.898 --> 00:23:20.482
Yearnments.

242
00:23:32.202 --> 00:23:34.079
Hello?

243
00:25:08.799 --> 00:25:12.636
- Good morning. Sisters.
Today a new life begins.

244
00:25:13.554 --> 00:25:15.139
But this new year will not be easy.

245
00:25:15.931 --> 00:25:17.808
You will question your purpose.

246
00:25:17.850 --> 00:25:21.311
You will question me
and why you have come here.

247
00:25:21.979 --> 00:25:25.607
And some of you will not have
the spiritual fortitude for this life.

248
00:25:27.818 --> 00:25:29.361
- What did she say?

249
00:25:29.403 --> 00:25:31.405
- God is good.
God is great.

250
00:25:31.447 --> 00:25:33.032
- God. my head hurts.

251
00:25:33.073 --> 00:25:34.783
- Too much blood of Christ?

252
00:25:38.162 --> 00:25:40.205
- Do you find this amusing.
Sister Guendalina?

253
00:25:41.415 --> 00:25:42.750
- No. forgive me.

254
00:25:42.791 --> 00:25:44.752
- This side of the room is with me.

255
00:25:45.502 --> 00:25:49.423
The other.
will serve with Sister Isabelle.

256
00:25:49.923 --> 00:25:51.592
- No.

257
00:25:54.011 --> 00:25:55.763
- What a blessing
to mentor you both.

258
00:25:55.804 --> 00:25:57.639
Finish eating.
We have work to do.

259
00:25:58.098 --> 00:26:00.017
- Looks like her vibrator
ran out of battery.

260
00:26:00.309 --> 00:26:01.977
- What does that mean?

261
00:26:02.019 --> 00:26:03.729
- Oh. nothing.
I really like her.

262
00:26:03.771 --> 00:26:05.981
I'm super excited.

263
00:26:06.023 --> 00:26:07.775
- Clean their back thoroughly.

264
00:26:07.816 --> 00:26:10.819
